    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When you choose this path at 2nd Level, you gain the E-Rank Genjutsu, Mind Sliver.</p><p> If you already know this genjutsu, you learn a different E-Rank genjutsu of your choice.</p><p> The genjutsu you learn this way does not count against your number of jutsu known.</p><p> When you would cast Mind Sliver, it gains the Unaware keyword, and they subtract 1d6 from their next saving throw, instead of 1d4.</p><p> Genjutsu you cast with the Unaware keyword, has its DC increased by +1.</p><p> This bonus increases to +2 at 10th and +3 at 19th levels.</p><p></p>",
